  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We are the Entity Investigation & Research Institute.</h2>You just got hired by EIRI; researching and battling the Visitors, unknown entities that have invaded our world. A dark sci-fi dungeon crawling RPG with themes of exploration and survival.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/5491fd4be5efd00ffb8ed49b00f73e9d.poster.avif?t=1726610092\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/5491fd4be5efd00ffb8ed49b00f73e9d.webm?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore:</strong> Investigate procedurally generated maps for entities and items. Improve your loadout with over 180 standard items and countless randomized Uniques.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/4b0b3d9bb2464ee196a84e32625c850e.poster.avif?t=1726610092\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/4b0b3d9bb2464ee196a84e32625c850e.webm?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/4b0b3d9bb2464ee196a84e32625c850e.mp4?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Research:</strong> Discover more about the entities to unlock over 20 different moves with unique Critical bonuses. With over 150 standard entities, extra randomized bosses and elite modifiers the threat is imminent.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/af1313bce3f70547a9f27b052458b485.poster.avif?t=1726610092\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/af1313bce3f70547a9f27b052458b485.webm?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/af1313bce3f70547a9f27b052458b485.mp4?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Battle:</strong> Destroy entities to gain XP, currency and items, unlock and defeat bosses to receive high rarity rewards. With hybrid real-time/turn-based combat every second counts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hybrid real-time/turn-based battles.<br></li><li>Random maps.<br></li><li>90 basic entities and 60 bosses.<br></li><li>10 secret entities.<br></li><li>Random Unique items and 180+ standard items.<br></li><li>20+ moves with unique Critical bonuses.<br></li><li>Random Bounty bosses.<br></li><li>Hardcore mode.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/4d22a73b1833270144d84346a24e75ab.poster.avif?t=1726610092\" width=600 height=211 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562230/extras/4d22a73b1833270144d84346a24e75ab.webm?t=1726610092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
